rComments: Jeanie is a great teach and mentor and in the two classes I took with her, she helped me improve my French skills tremendously. She works so hard as a teacher and she expects an equal amount of effort from her students. The classroom atmosphere is always one of respect and tolerance, as well as fun and enjoyable.
Jeanie is super enthusiastic about her work. She is always super thrilled to be teaching. Even though grammar can be a pain, she really helped. I definitely enjoyed her class.
